de.uos.dgrlvq
Class DataProcessor

java.lang.Object
  de.uos.dgrlvq.DataProcessor
public class DataProcessor
extends java.lang.Object

This class is a helper for the generation of pattern matrices. An object of this class can parse the pattern file, allocates system variables, construct the 3D pattern matries, construct relevance vector lambda etc.

Author:
Gulraj Singh Mrok, University Osnabrück, Germany
